{"tid":566032,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"C朗睇利記 魔迷唔高興","createTime":"2018-02-19T14:38:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-19T16:07:58.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f42d6fae8d15281468554f9053cd3ebf32999b43","tid":566032,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T14:38:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-sports.now.com/sport/news/4/284/20430633284/20440080277_600x389.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-sports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F4%2F284%2F20430633284%2F20440080277_600x389.jpg&h=1b82c633&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=nDg5AbBySp3qGS%2FW34J3tjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=b4ce6fcf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】一日紅魔，一世紅魔？大紅人基斯坦奴朗拿度近日在社交網站的短片，引起前東家曼聯粉絲不滿，原因何在？<br />\n<br />\n周日西甲又入波的33歲超級巨星基斯坦奴朗拿度（Cristiano Ronaldo），不經不覺由曼聯改投皇家馬德里已經9年，日前與女友洛迪古絲一邊擲波波，一邊看電視，並上載短片與網民分享。<br />\n<br />\n只是背景惹禍，C朗和女友被發現正在觀看歐聯利物浦大勝波圖的賽事，導致被部份魔迷留言「投訴」，認為他不該欣賞曼聯死敵利物浦的比賽。其實，上載短片的是洛迪古絲，而非C朗，而且大紅人好勝心強，一直專心擲波波，未必專注看球賽。魔迷是否太緊張？<br />\n<br />\n最近，C朗狀態已有起色，歐聯16強首回合對巴黎聖日耳門時梅開二度領軍輕取3:1，而他剛在西甲對貝迪斯亦有入球。<br />\n<br />\n相關片段：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=toYkSGx3sFE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DtoYkSGx3sFE&d=nDg5AbBySp3qGS%2FW34J3tjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=8c2c5d29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=toYkSGx3sFE</a><br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : Instagram圖片"},{"pid":"205064de0685f24034a00e9c9d4e4b517d439a39","tid":566032,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T14:47:47.000Z","msg":"49000又嚟"},{"pid":"56d770ad07da3f951e14d5a648c7c1f7d6a1484d","tid":566032,"uid":1991,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T14:52:46.000Z","msg":"成日話人怨婦 今次真係唔知邊個怨婦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/asse